                       <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#2r"/>
                           <desc type="DonationNote">(upper margin) Donation note, written in a very crude hand. It
                              states that the manuscript was donated to the <placeName ref="INS0105DD">Dabra Dāmmo monastery</placeName> by ʾAbbā
                              Gabra Krǝstos and his son ʾAbbā Gabra Mikāʾel.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአባ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወወልዱ፡ አባ፡ ገብረ፡
